TI  - Rehydration Beverages Made from Quercus sideroxyla Infusion, Probiotics, and Prebiotics: Antioxidant and Anti-Inflammatory Potential
PY  - 2025
T2  - Foods
VL  - 14
IS  - 5
C7  - 837
