TI  - From wheat gluten wastewater to functional biscuits: Extraction, characterization, and application of water-unextractable arabinoxylan in low-GI fermented biscuits
PY  - 2025
T2  - International Journal of Biological Macromolecules
VL  - 321
C7  - 146438
